title: The Henderson Kids II
overview: The Henderson family finds a new home in the bayside suburb of Westport, but the neighbourhood is not as serene as it seems.  The Henderson Kids have to face the Brown Street Boys – the toughest BMX gang in town; there are shady characters lurking in the suburb, and then Wal disappears.  With friends at their side and a mystery before them, life is bound to be an adventure.
